## ✅ Step 6: `CODEOWNERS`

### 🔍 Navigation:
1. Create a `.github` folder in your repo.
2. Inside `.github`, create a file named `CODEOWNERS`.

### 📋 Copy-Paste Template:
```plaintext
# UI Components
client/src/components/ui/* @odom45

# Payout Logic
server/* @odom45

# Config & Deployment
*.config.* @odom45
